{"tid":381611,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[明天九月一日]19歲IVE生 留遺書藍田墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-08-31T05:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:01:37.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d97948debbc0b2ca0daa062d218f4f18db48efa","tid":381611,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170831/57150528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170831%2F57150528&d=EVU0uj8QfCgFZij4OLs6aMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ac43e201\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170831%2F57150528&h=0df0ec4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170831/57150528</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19歲IVE生 留遺書藍田墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n【13：30更新】下午1時左右，死者10多名親友在場拜祭。<br />\n【11：30更新】新增動新聞<br />\n【10：0更新】死者是香港專業教育學院學生<br />\n<br />\n藍田德田邨德欣樓，清晨5時許，一名姓林19歲青年，被保安員發現從高處墮下，口吐鮮血重創昏迷。救護員接報到場急救後，將傷者送聯合醫院搶救，惟終告不治。警員封鎖現場展開調查，相信死者從住所單位墮下，警員稍後發現遺書，初步認為案件並無可疑。<br />\n據悉，死者在香港專業教育學院就讀，惟尋死原因有待進一步了解。早上7時許，死者父母及多名親友到醫院了解，其中一名年邁女親友情緒激動，要由親友攙扶，認屍後更哭成淚人。"},{"pid":"2e99dc08cdbd182773a9d5fc0b9cf4d3bd055568","tid":381611,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8798e4ca6edb6d8f7d86dbc066bb41f1ac39605e","tid":381611,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"Ive&hellip;&hellip; 明智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死亡係解脫"},{"pid":"d10c1c60c7f9389d3744031ec8041866ed19ec34","tid":381611,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"關唔關ocamp事🙊"}]}